VARIOUS CHRISTIAN MINISTRIES - 225 SERMONS
--------------------------------------------------------------

This is an assorted collection of 225 sermons by 18 different individuals including Chuck Missler, Greg Laurie, Warren Wiersbe, Lasserre Bradley Jr, Hank Hanegraaff, David McGee, Rick Warren, John MacArthur, Chuck Swindoll, Ken Davis, Chip Ingram, James Dobson, John MacArthur, Ron Jones, James Boice, Colin Smith, Max Lucado, and James MacDonald.

God Bless,
